And the holy land of Europe

00:06:55.480 --> 00:06:58.840
has got lots of water in it, flowing.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:03.480
It's at a lower level than the Mother Earth

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:07.999
and the sea flows through it.

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:16.320
So it's a good combination of the sea and the earth here.

00:07:16.999 --> 00:07:20.480
So sea cleanses

00:07:22.999 --> 00:07:27.999
and the Mother Earth blesses the people of Holland,

00:07:29.200 --> 00:07:35.000
But if they have lost their moorings

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:39.840
and they are flying in the wrong direction,

00:07:39.999 --> 00:07:45.440
then the same holy land can become a hell land.

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:50.999
So we have to be very careful

00:07:51.160 --> 00:07:56.480
to see that we create more and more Sahaja Yogis in this place.

00:07:57.999 --> 00:08:02.400
In My reading of the character of the western people

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:07.320
I find they are extremely aggressive by nature

00:08:07.480 --> 00:08:10.999
and very egoistical on the whole.

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:14.240
One should not feel that I am saying about you, but I'm saying.

00:08:14.440 --> 00:08:17.000
You are Sahaja yogis, you belong to the Kingdom of God

00:08:17.320 --> 00:08:20.999
but I'm telling about in general now.

00:08:23.999 --> 00:08:25.840
While I'm talking keep your eyes open.

00:08:25.999 --> 00:08:30.480
I don't know why people close the eyes, this I can't understand.

00:08:31.360 --> 00:08:36.200
Now when we are in the holy land,

00:08:39.480 --> 00:08:45.999
we find that the Mother Earth has allowed the sea to flow in,

00:08:47.999 --> 00:08:52.200
and is a very good place for Me to say something to you.

00:08:53.999 --> 00:08:59.320
Here the sea has taken refuge in the Mother.

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:06.480
The guru has bound itself with the motherly qualities.

00:09:08.120 --> 00:09:11.480
A person feels more safe on the ground

00:09:11.999 --> 00:09:15.999
than on the sea or in the air.

00:09:17.480 --> 00:09:21.480
So today is the best opportunity for Me to say

00:09:21.999 --> 00:09:24.320
that after the Guru Puja,

00:09:24.999 --> 00:09:28.999
we have to understand that to be holy means

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:32.240
you must allow

00:09:32.440 --> 00:09:35.840
the guru tattwa to circulate

00:09:35.999 --> 00:09:39.200
in the Mother principle.

00:09:39.999 --> 00:09:45.480
Or the guru tattwa is to be controlled and guided and beautified

00:09:45.999 --> 00:09:49.999
by the Mother principle.

00:09:51.480 --> 00:09:54.960
It's only the Mother Earth that is beautiful

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.999
because it can create so many varieties,

00:09:58.200 --> 00:10:00.480
so many dramas, so many places.

00:10:00.999 --> 00:10:04.999
Any other element, if you see, has nothing in it.

00:10:06.120 --> 00:10:09.320
So it is She who can create.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:14.360
So we should take to the motherly quality more

00:10:14.999 --> 00:10:18.999
and try to bind our guru principle

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:23.400
through that Motherly, beautiful, creative power,

00:10:24.999 --> 00:10:31.440
so that we make our presence very agreeable,

00:10:33.280 --> 00:10:37.840
very congenial, very beautiful,

00:10:37.999 --> 00:10:40.000
full of interest and varieties;

00:10:40.320 --> 00:10:43.840
every time new flowers, every time new fruits,

00:10:43.999 --> 00:10:48.480
every time a new, new design.

00:10:50.160 --> 00:10:53.160
As Kundalini is made of Mother Earth,

00:10:53.360 --> 00:10:56.240
we are quite capable of doing that.

00:10:57.120 --> 00:11:01.320
There are gurus and gurus and gurus but no one so far

00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:05.480
is such a master as you are of the Kundalini.

00:11:06.920 --> 00:11:11.240
If they were they would have given Realization to thousands.

00:11:11.999 --> 00:11:17.999
Why? Because your Mother has penetrated into your guru principle.

00:11:20.999 --> 00:11:22.840
And has risen your Kundalini,

00:11:22.999 --> 00:11:24.999
has given you powers to raise Kundalini,

00:11:25.240 --> 00:11:28.999
breaking your seventh chakra, so clearly.

00:11:29.999 --> 00:11:32.480
That never happened with anyone.

00:11:32.999 --> 00:11:37.999
Even incarnations could not do that to the masses, as you are doing.

00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:40.999
Kundalini is flowing from your hand;

00:11:41.400 --> 00:11:44.440
the Ganesha is active in you,

00:11:44.999 --> 00:11:49.840
but it should never give you the ego,

00:11:49.999 --> 00:11:56.240
or the sternness or the heaviness of the sea.

00:11:57.480 --> 00:12:00.999
But it should give you the beauty of the Mother Earth.

00:12:01.440 --> 00:12:06.999
Mother Earth is always bigger than the sea,

00:12:07.280 --> 00:12:09.840
because She has to contain the sea.

00:12:09.999 --> 00:12:13.480
Sea can never be bigger than the Mother Earth.

00:12:14.240 --> 00:12:16.840
Sometimes it looks, sea, bigger

00:12:16.999 --> 00:12:19.240
but sea is contained in the Mother Earth.

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:21.960
It cannot go beyond.

00:12:22.120 --> 00:12:27.999
So Mother Earth is always greater, bigger, wider than the sea.

00:12:29.480 --> 00:12:32.999
So one has to understand that when Kundalini has risen,

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:35.200
you have become all of the seven chakras

00:12:35.440 --> 00:12:37.999
and not only the guru chakra.

00:12:38.999 --> 00:12:41.840
And when you have become the guru chakra

00:12:41.999 --> 00:12:47.320
it is also bounded on all sides by the Mother Earth.

00:12:49.200 --> 00:12:51.999
Under these circumstances,

00:12:52.200 --> 00:12:54.480
when we are so capable,

00:12:54.960 --> 00:12:57.480
we are giving Realization to so many people,

00:12:57.999 --> 00:13:00.840
when we are achieving so many things,

00:13:00.999 --> 00:13:07.480
if we could just become humble, congenial, beautiful,

00:13:08.400 --> 00:13:11.480
we can master the whole world.

00:13:11.999 --> 00:13:16.440
But I find in the styles of Sahaja yogis, especially in the west,

00:13:17.160 --> 00:13:20.000
and westernized Indians,

00:13:20.320 --> 00:13:22.999
there is so much of ego still expressed

00:13:23.200 --> 00:13:25.999
in their talks, in their behavior.

00:13:26.999 --> 00:13:30.480
They are not capable of it, to see I think sometimes,

00:13:30.999 --> 00:13:33.999
but better see it.

00:13:34.999 --> 00:13:38.999
First you may have to act as sweet people, maybe,

00:13:40.960 --> 00:13:43.920
but you must learn that way.

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:47.320
If you do not understand that all your leadership,

00:13:47.480 --> 00:13:51.440
all your guru tattwa depends entirely

00:13:51.920 --> 00:13:57.480
on the loving capacity of your Mother, Her patience.

00:13:58.000 --> 00:14:01.999
I get angry but perhaps once in a ten years or twelve years,

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:06.000
something like that, seldom.

00:14:07.960 --> 00:14:10.320
That's better, then the anger has some meaning.

00:14:10.480 --> 00:14:13.840
But all the time if you are in a temper or you try to show off

00:14:13.999 --> 00:14:15.840
or if you have so much of ego

00:14:15.999 --> 00:14:18.840
that you go on asserting on wrong things,

00:14:18.999 --> 00:14:21.240
then you cannot be effective.

00:14:21.960 --> 00:14:26.240
Another thing I've seen, that ego has no discretion.

00:14:26.999 --> 00:14:30.840
Ego has no discretion of any kind.

00:14:30.999 --> 00:14:34.999
If you are egoistical, first thing you lose is discretion.

00:14:36.320 --> 00:14:39.200
Then what's the use of having this nonsense of a ego?

00:14:39.400 --> 00:14:41.960
which doesn't give you discretion?

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:45.999
And people who have greater ego always then assert

00:14:46.280 --> 00:14:49.000
and you have to agree to that.

00:14:49.999 --> 00:14:51.320
You are more impressed by the people

00:14:51.480 --> 00:14:54.999
who have greater ego than yours.

00:14:55.480 --> 00:14:59.840
And you like the people who are without any ego

00:14:59.999 --> 00:15:02.480
so you can oppress on them.

00:15:02.999 --> 00:15:05.840
But the discretion part is very poor, that you can see.

00:15:05.999 --> 00:15:09.320
The other day one guru had come, the one gentleman had come,

00:15:09.480 --> 00:15:13.920
and he has given some mantra by his guru.

00:15:14.400 --> 00:15:16.840
Now, he can't hear anything against his guru.  Why?

00:15:17.000 --> 00:15:20.480
Because his ego has chosen that guru.

00:15:20.999 --> 00:15:23.320
Because the ego has chosen how can the ego be wrong?

00:15:23.480 --> 00:15:27.999
And ego is always wrong, invariably it is wrong.

00:15:29.200 --> 00:15:32.999
Everything is upside down with the ego-orientation.

00:15:33.280 --> 00:15:36.280
Gradually you will learn that in the west

00:15:36.480 --> 00:15:41.000
people lack common sense,

00:15:41.320 --> 00:15:44.320
completely they lack common sense, in everything.

00:15:44.480 --> 00:15:45.999
I mean if they had common sense

00:15:46.200 --> 00:15:48.000
there would have been much less problems.

00:15:48.320 --> 00:15:49.840
But common sense is lacking

00:15:49.999 --> 00:15:52.840
and also I find the same thing in Sahaja yogis.

00:15:52.999 --> 00:15:54.840
They lack common sense.

00:15:54.999 --> 00:15:59.840
You have to become so wise, that common sense should be your nature.

00:15:59.999 --> 00:16:02.200
But common sense we lack.

00:16:02.400 --> 00:16:05.840
Like today, (I`ll have some water)

00:16:05.999 --> 00:16:11.999
today I was discussing about say, the labor problem,

00:16:12.480 --> 00:16:16.960
which is a very general problem,

00:16:23.999 --> 00:16:26.120
which is a very general problem.

00:16:26.360 --> 00:16:30.240
You have a labor problem.  For example you have unemployment.

00:16:30.999 --> 00:16:33.480
Now the whole system that is built in here

00:16:33.920 --> 00:16:37.280
and we too have adopted some of it but not to that extent,

00:16:37.480 --> 00:16:40.999
of working hours, is very absurd.

00:16:42.480 --> 00:16:45.440
For example, supposing you get up at four o'clock.

00:16:45.920 --> 00:16:49.999
I mean that's very big supposition, of course, but

00:16:50.320 --> 00:16:54.999
supposing we get up at four and we take our bath.

00:16:55.480 --> 00:16:58.000
Morning time is very peaceful, we can meditate,

00:16:58.320 --> 00:16:59.480
we can do what we like.

00:16:59.960 --> 00:17:02.200
Then we finish all the other work we have to do,

00:17:02.440 --> 00:17:06.320
get yourself ready, have yourself ready,

00:17:06.480 --> 00:17:11.320
have your breakfast or tea or whatever you want to have.

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:14.840
Then by eight o'clock you are ready for work.

00:17:14.999 --> 00:17:18.400
Supposing you go at eight o'clock for your work.

00:17:20.999 --> 00:17:27.400
So you can work from eight up to one o'clock very easily,

00:17:28.440 --> 00:17:30.999
very easily, no problem.

00:17:31.280 --> 00:17:34.320
Then one o'clock you come back home,

00:17:34.480 --> 00:17:37.999
have your lunch and have a siesta.

00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:44.480
If you can have siesta for about two hours,

00:17:44.999 --> 00:17:50.400
say three, till four o'clock , by five o'clock you again go to work.

00:17:51.360 --> 00:17:55.280
Then you can work from five to eleven without feeling tired at all.

00:17:55.480 --> 00:17:57.480
After eleven you might be.

00:17:57.999 --> 00:18:00.999
So you put in much more work,

00:18:01.999 --> 00:18:07.280
much less sleep and you keep fresh and young.

00:18:08.000 --> 00:18:10.999
But it is, it requires common sense.

00:18:11.440 --> 00:18:14.000
Now the, how unemployment can be solved;

00:18:14.320 --> 00:18:18.920
some people can work in the morning, some can work in the evening.

00:18:19.480 --> 00:18:22.320
Now those who are working in the morning,

00:18:22.480 --> 00:18:26.480
the ladies could be in the house, men could be outside.

00:18:26.999 --> 00:18:29.320
Then the men come out in the evening,

00:18:29.480 --> 00:18:30.999
they can do the household work.

00:18:31.200 --> 00:18:33.440
Ladies can do in their house

00:18:33.960 --> 00:18:39.360
or when they are in the house, men can do creative work,

00:18:39.960 --> 00:18:42.999
like making statutes, hand work,

00:18:43.999 --> 00:18:46.440
hand-made things.

00:18:46.920 --> 00:18:50.200
So everybody gets employment.

00:18:50.999 --> 00:18:55.999
They became more creative,  much happier people

00:18:57.480 --> 00:19:00.999
and so easy to solve the problem.

00:19:02.999 --> 00:19:04.840
But there is unemployment;

00:19:04.999 --> 00:19:07.480
Because of unemployment there are so many problems.

00:19:08.120 --> 00:19:10.840
Very easy to solve the problem of unemployment.

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:13.840
You don't give any social security or anything.

00:19:13.999 --> 00:19:18.999
You give them their pay and let them work for shorter time.

00:19:20.240 --> 00:19:23.840
If you make them create things and sell them,

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:26.480
they have more money

00:19:26.999 --> 00:19:29.999
or they can have nice things around them.

00:19:31.320 --> 00:19:35.999
Otherwise you can have horrid things like that.

00:19:37.999 --> 00:19:42.200
So you can have lots of things which are hand-made,

00:19:42.999 --> 00:19:45.080
plus machine-made things, whatever you want to have.

00:19:45.280 --> 00:19:48.320
There should be a balance. With common sense we should know

00:19:48.480 --> 00:19:52.480
how far to go, how far to have balance.

00:19:52.999 --> 00:19:56.480
Like machine goes on like mad; we cannot control machines.

00:19:56.960 --> 00:19:58.840
Because we think we get money, we do not.

00:19:59.000 --> 00:20:02.200
After some time machines have to stop.

00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:08.480
So you have to go up to...

00:20:08.999 --> 00:20:14.240
This, I'm trying to put the guru tattwa into the Mother tattwa,

00:20:21.360 --> 00:20:24.480
as practical.

00:20:29.360 --> 00:20:34.120
So common sense should be applied

00:20:34.320 --> 00:20:37.480
and that can only come when there is no ego.

00:20:37.920 --> 00:20:40.000
With ego that cannot be common sense

00:20:40.280 --> 00:20:44.400
"Because I like it, I do it".  But this "I" is a ego who is blind,

00:20:44.960 --> 00:20:47.480
who is indiscreet, who is stupid.

00:20:47.999 --> 00:20:50.999
So ultimately we do stupid things.

00:20:52.999 --> 00:20:55.320
There should be common sense,

00:20:55.480 --> 00:21:00.000
which one can learn by getting rid of this ego.

00:21:02.999 --> 00:21:06.999
Now people say, "Mother, how to get rid of ego?"

00:21:09.000 --> 00:21:13.840
It's very simple, you have to move left to the right 108 times,

00:21:14.000 --> 00:21:15.240
in Sahaja yoga.

00:21:15.440 --> 00:21:18.440
You have to forgive people, in Sahaja Yoga.

00:21:18.999 --> 00:21:21.840
And you can watch yourself.  First of all, see,

00:21:21.999 --> 00:21:25.400
do you watch others or you watch yourself?  First of all.

00:21:27.480 --> 00:21:32.200
Like there was a lady traveling with Me, very old lady.

00:21:33.320 --> 00:21:36.840
And she said, "This man is handsome.

00:21:37.000 --> 00:21:39.480
This man is not handsome.

00:21:39.960 --> 00:21:43.480
This woman is good looking, she is pretty", that way.

00:21:43.999 --> 00:21:47.480
I was looking at her.  I said "This mad woman,

00:21:47.999 --> 00:21:50.960
she will go really crazy by the time we get down.

00:21:51.120 --> 00:21:54.240
She goes on looking into every person, judging everyone,

00:21:54.440 --> 00:21:56.200
who is handsome, who is not."

00:21:56.400 --> 00:22:00.000
And everybody whom she called handsome I found him ugly.

00:22:01.400 --> 00:22:06.480
So I gave up. I said "You better decide I never tried these things".

00:22:07.360 --> 00:22:11.840
Then, "That man is not good, he is very hot tempered,

00:22:11.999 --> 00:22:14.320
he is this thing, he is that,

00:22:14.480 --> 00:22:16.999
he talks like that, he walks like that,

00:22:17.200 --> 00:22:19.280
he shouldn't do, look like that",

00:22:19.480 --> 00:22:22.000
worried about other people.

00:22:22.999 --> 00:22:26.240
You tell them anything, they'll go on shaking their neck like that,

00:22:26.440 --> 00:22:31.240
"Oh, how could you do it?"  But you do it yourselves.

00:22:33.160 --> 00:22:36.999
If they have to say yes, they'll do it ten times, "yes, yes, yes".

00:22:37.480 --> 00:22:40.999
If they have to say no, they'll go on saying: "no, no, no, no, no".

00:22:43.999 --> 00:22:46.999
There is no common sense.

00:22:49.960 --> 00:22:52.840
Why to move your neck so many times.

00:22:53.000 --> 00:22:57.000
See if somebody is saying that, you need not react all the time.

00:22:57.360 --> 00:23:00.240
So this is another thing, is internal reaction.

00:23:00.440 --> 00:23:03.840
First is external, seeing everyone, judging everyone,

00:23:04.000 --> 00:23:07.320
"Oh, I don't like this station; this is too much dusty".

00:23:07.480 --> 00:23:10.320
"This bathroom is not good, that room is not good,

00:23:10.480 --> 00:23:14.160
that thing is not good", like that go on,

00:23:14.999 --> 00:23:18.000
as if you are the Queen of England.

00:23:18.999 --> 00:23:21.999
Even that could be even more than that

00:23:22.240 --> 00:23:25.320
because she is not even allowed to choose her dress;

00:23:25.480 --> 00:23:28.999
Parliament has to decide.

00:23:33.999 --> 00:23:37.960
Poor thing cannot have any ego at all, poor thing.

00:23:38.320 --> 00:23:40.320
She has to choose what dress she has to wear

00:23:40.480 --> 00:23:42.480
for a particular occasion;

00:23:42.999 --> 00:23:47.480
If the Parliament says yes, she wears.  She says no, no.

00:23:50.280 --> 00:23:52.840
big problem, for them.

00:23:52.999 --> 00:23:57.320
But for us, who are free people, we must have common sense

00:23:57.480 --> 00:24:01.840
to understand what to do, where to do, what to talk, how to talk.

00:24:01.999 --> 00:24:04.999
But when there is ego, you cannot have common sense.

00:24:05.280 --> 00:24:07.200
And this is the reason I think

00:24:07.440 --> 00:24:11.440
the western people have become so stupid in so many things.

00:24:12.160 --> 00:24:15.240
Whatever I see, I see it's upside down.

00:24:15.480 --> 00:24:18.320
Indians, we may be poor people, in the villages.

00:24:18.480 --> 00:24:21.840
They are not so educated. You are all very well educated people,

00:24:21.999 --> 00:24:25.999
everything is there, but all has come out of ego.

00:24:26.999 --> 00:24:29.999
So the common sense is lacking.

00:24:32.960 --> 00:24:35.320
So those who deal with the Mother Earth, like farmers are,

00:24:35.480 --> 00:24:38.400
have tremendous common sense.

00:24:39.160 --> 00:24:42.320
Now in Holland I used to think people will have

00:24:42.480 --> 00:24:45.480
lot of common sense, because they are farmers you see.

00:24:46.320 --> 00:24:49.960
When I had come in '65, they were better off, much better people,

00:24:50.120 --> 00:24:52.400
not so nonsensical.

00:24:52.999 --> 00:24:57.240
They were well dressed, nice, sensible, solid people.

00:24:57.480 --> 00:25:00.999
Of course I met quite elderly people also, I should say,

00:25:01.480 --> 00:25:03.320
but I was surprised that in the market

00:25:03.480 --> 00:25:05.999
you could not get a transistor made in Holland ,

00:25:06.240 --> 00:25:08.999
could not get anything made in Holland.

00:25:09.400 --> 00:25:12.320
So I said, "How is it? You don't make anything, machines?"

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:16.000
They said, "Why should we? For our twenty-five bulbs of tulips,

00:25:16.280 --> 00:25:20.840
- in those days - we get one transistor from Japan.

00:25:20.999 --> 00:25:24.999
So why should we make a transistor?"  Common sense.

00:25:25.999 --> 00:25:28.240
"We send from here twenty five bulbs".

00:25:28.480 --> 00:25:32.960
And they had fields and fields of all kinds of tulips,

00:25:33.120 --> 00:25:35.840
all over, I mean when I came here. So they said,

00:25:36.000 --> 00:25:39.320
"For twenty-five bulbs we get one transistor so why should we?

00:25:39.480 --> 00:25:43.999
We export our bulbs to them and get their transistors.

00:25:44.440 --> 00:25:47.999
Why should we make transistors?"

00:25:49.999 --> 00:25:53.000
Then they said "We export our cheese to a particular country,

00:25:53.400 --> 00:25:56.320
our eggs to Italy , our chicken to this country

00:25:56.480 --> 00:25:58.999
and we get all that we need."

00:26:00.000 --> 00:26:05.840
I was amazed you see. They are so, so proud of their agriculture

00:26:05.999 --> 00:26:07.840
and so much doing that way,

00:26:07.999 --> 00:26:10.240
which was a very sensible thing and because

00:26:10.440 --> 00:26:12.999
they were dealing with the land I thought I'll find

00:26:13.240 --> 00:26:15.960
Holland people to be the best.

00:26:16.440 --> 00:26:18.320
But then I got reports that people are

00:26:18.480 --> 00:26:21.000
absolutely gone off their heads.

00:26:21.360 --> 00:26:24.999
They have become like bullocks now

00:26:27.920 --> 00:26:31.120
Working with the land they have become

00:26:31.320 --> 00:26:33.999
like bullocks who plough the land.

00:26:34.480 --> 00:26:38.999
I was surprised "How have they become like bulls?"

00:26:39.999 --> 00:26:43.400
They were very sensible people, very sensible.

00:26:44.000 --> 00:26:48.999
Farmers, sensibly dealing with things

00:26:49.999 --> 00:26:52.480
and working out things

00:26:53.480 --> 00:26:55.999
in such a beautiful manner,

00:26:56.480 --> 00:27:00.960
very innocent and simple people and naive,

00:27:01.360 --> 00:27:05.320
up to a point of sweetness, very sweet.

00:27:05.480 --> 00:27:08.320
When we came here they wanted to please us,

00:27:08.480 --> 00:27:12.480
so they wanted to put a flag for us or for our country.

00:27:12.999 --> 00:27:15.999
And they put Pakistan's flag in front of us.

00:27:25.999 --> 00:27:28.840
So I was very happy to see that.

00:27:28.999 --> 00:27:31.280
And they were talking of vegetarianism.

00:27:31.480 --> 00:27:34.280
But when we came, my daughter had suddenly become vegetarian

00:27:34.480 --> 00:27:36.320
because she had developed a funny nausea

00:27:36.480 --> 00:27:38.960
in the, in the ship, you see.

00:27:39.120 --> 00:27:41.000
So she was not eating any meat or like that.

00:27:41.280 --> 00:27:43.840
So she said "We are, I am vegetarian".

00:27:44.000 --> 00:27:47.999
So they said, "All right, then will you have chicken?"

00:27:48.200 --> 00:27:51.999
They were that simple you know, very simple people.

00:27:52.920 --> 00:27:54.840
And now they are talking about vegetarianism.

00:27:54.999 --> 00:27:58.280
I am surprised. Since '65 and '85 only,

00:27:58.480 --> 00:28:01.480
these twenty years, how much they are changed.

00:28:03.240 --> 00:28:08.960
Very nice. And they were not busy doing all these exercises,

00:28:09.120 --> 00:28:12.840
and reducing weight or increasing weight and jogging on the road.

00:28:12.999 --> 00:28:16.840
Just now, yesterday, I was walking, everybody was jogging like mad.

00:28:16.999 --> 00:28:22.999
Very sensible, but they have lost their common sense.

00:28:23.999 --> 00:28:26.840
Because perhaps they do not come in contact with Mother Earth,

00:28:26.999 --> 00:28:30.960
they are using machines too much, maybe that is one of the reasons.

00:28:31.320 --> 00:28:34.240
And must be the air from other outside countries coming

00:28:34.440 --> 00:28:36.999
and they think "They are rustic", so they must accept

00:28:37.160 --> 00:28:41.480
that is all that is modern, sophisticated, perhaps, maybe.

00:28:45.000 --> 00:28:50.999
There is a story about a farmer, who was traveling by train.

00:28:51.920 --> 00:28:54.320
And there were some naughty boys who came from the city

00:28:54.480 --> 00:28:57.999
so they wanted to pull the legs of the farmer.

00:28:58.960 --> 00:29:02.840
So one of the boys asked him that "If the eggs

00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:06.440
are selling here

00:29:06.920 --> 00:29:10.480
in this station for 20 p

00:29:10.999 --> 00:29:14.960
and in the next station the chicken is selling for one pound,

00:29:15.120 --> 00:29:17.320
what is my age?"

00:29:17.480 --> 00:29:19.960
Just to tease him.

00:29:20.160 --> 00:29:24.480
So immediately the fellow says "You must be twenty-two".

00:29:25.160 --> 00:29:28.320
He said "How do you know exactly if I am twenty-two?"

00:29:28.480 --> 00:29:34.200
He said "Because my brother who is full mad, is forty-four."

00:29:47.999 --> 00:29:51.840
Can you see? They are so practical, so "brass".

00:29:51.999 --> 00:29:54.840
You see, as you call in American language "brass tacks", you see.

00:29:54.999 --> 00:29:59.480
They know what is it. He looked at him and he said, "Twenty-two".

00:29:59.999 --> 00:30:06.240
He said, "How? Why?" "My brother, who is 44, is full mad".

00:30:07.480 --> 00:30:10.999
And these boys didn't know where to look, you see,

00:30:11.360 --> 00:30:13.999
because they wanted to tease him.

00:30:16.280 --> 00:30:18.999
And the farmers have great sense.

00:30:19.320 --> 00:30:22.480
Like we had one minister who had developed a bad neck, you see,

00:30:22.920 --> 00:30:25.240
wild Vishuddhi. He was Chief Minister.

00:30:25.440 --> 00:30:27.960
He used to go on like this, his head used to go like this.

00:30:28.120 --> 00:30:30.840
So some farmers came to see him.

00:30:31.000 --> 00:30:35.240
They saw him and they looked at him.

00:30:35.480 --> 00:30:37.840
They said, "Oh, he's saying no already,

00:30:37.999 --> 00:30:42.240
what's the use of telling him anything?"

00:30:42.480 --> 00:30:45.480
We have lots of stories of farmers in India,

00:30:45.999 --> 00:30:48.999
which shows how much they understand life.

00:30:49.160 --> 00:30:51.840
I had a very nice gardener.

00:30:51.999 --> 00:30:53.840
He was from a village.

00:30:53.999 --> 00:30:58.280
So there was one fellow, old fellow,

00:30:58.999 --> 00:31:00.840
another gardener.

00:31:01.000 --> 00:31:04.480
He says, "No use talking to this old fellow". I said, "Why?"

00:31:04.999 --> 00:31:08.160
He said "If he is a Hindu,

00:31:08.360 --> 00:31:11.920
then an old man is a gone case."
I said "Why?"

00:31:12.080 --> 00:31:14.920
"Because in young age they live like

00:31:15.080 --> 00:31:17.480
ascetics and in old age they become like bhoots.

00:31:17.999 --> 00:31:21.840
But if he is a Muslim, they don't live like ascetics in young age.

00:31:21.999 --> 00:31:24.840
They enjoy life and in old age they are satisfied souls.

00:31:24.999 --> 00:31:29.480
So you better talk to a Muslim old man than to a Hindu old man."

00:31:30.400 --> 00:31:34.200
I mean their reading is so correct about things, you know.

00:31:34.480 --> 00:31:41.200
Everything that he said was so practical and so sensible.

00:31:41.999 --> 00:31:44.999
I was really surprised how he could say these things

00:31:45.240 --> 00:31:49.120
with such sweetness and with such goodness

00:31:49.320 --> 00:31:51.999
and how he understood so many things so well.

00:31:52.160 --> 00:31:55.840
And he was a very young fellow;

00:31:55.999 --> 00:31:58.999
about I would say thirty, thirty-two years of age.

00:31:59.240 --> 00:32:04.999
So he came to, he came to Bombay to see us.

00:32:05.480 --> 00:32:08.360
He didn't know our full address, he only knew Marine Drive.

00:32:08.960 --> 00:32:10.840
So he told the fellow, his taxi fellow,

00:32:10.999 --> 00:32:12.840
"You drive me at Marine Drive ".

00:32:12.999 --> 00:32:14.320
He said "Marine Drive is a big place".

00:32:14.480 --> 00:32:16.840
He said, "Drive me anywhere in Marine Drive "; he drove.

00:32:17.000 --> 00:32:19.840
So he went and asked "Is there a very tall

00:32:19.999 --> 00:32:22.840
gentleman staying in Marine Drive somewhere?"

00:32:22.999 --> 00:32:26.840
And you see, my husband is one of the tallest in Indians, you see.

00:32:26.999 --> 00:32:28.840
So he went to the servants, asked

00:32:28.999 --> 00:32:30.840
"Have you seen any tall sahib anywhere?"

00:32:30.999 --> 00:32:33.120
He said "There's one tallest staying there, you see".

00:32:33.320 --> 00:32:34.840
So that's how he came to our house.

00:32:35.000 --> 00:32:36.840
And he showed them his shoes, "These shoes

00:32:36.999 --> 00:32:39.480
given to me by my sahib. He is also very tall, you see".

00:32:39.960 --> 00:32:41.840
So he said "This shoe, he has given me,

00:32:41.999 --> 00:32:43.999
and he wears the same style of shoes".

00:32:44.200 --> 00:32:47.280
So servants noticed all these things and they were practical people.

00:32:47.480 --> 00:32:49.480
So another gardener who met him, he said

00:32:49.999 --> 00:32:52.920
"Yes, there's a tall fellow and he wears the same type of shoes".

00:32:53.080 --> 00:32:55.000
So he came to our house.

00:32:55.240 --> 00:33:00.840
How they are sharp and how their eyes are so penetrating,

00:33:00.999 --> 00:33:04.920
how they know everything about everything.

00:33:05.480 --> 00:33:07.840
It is remarkable,

00:33:07.999 --> 00:33:11.480
very remarkable and that is what we have to be.

00:33:11.999 --> 00:33:17.400
We have to be gurus with the Mother's influence on us.

00:33:17.999 --> 00:33:20.840
All the time the Mother controlling us, the Mother guiding us,

00:33:20.999 --> 00:33:23.840
the Mother making our banks, Mother making our maryadas.

00:33:23.999 --> 00:33:26.480
So the motherliness is your blessing.

00:33:26.999 --> 00:33:29.999
Today you are raising your Kundalini because your guru is a Mother.

00:33:30.240 --> 00:33:33.480
Otherwise you could never have done it.

00:33:35.920 --> 00:33:39.280
And that is why motherliness is so important.

00:33:40.280 --> 00:33:43.360
One of the reasons, perhaps, why the Sahaja yogis run away

00:33:43.920 --> 00:33:46.840
from the leaders and sometimes from the people

00:33:46.999 --> 00:33:50.840
who want to have follow-on may be that we do not know

00:33:50.999 --> 00:33:54.360
that they are just entering in, just opening out.

00:33:54.920 --> 00:33:56.999
So try to be kind, just hatching

00:33:57.160 --> 00:33:59.960
The little chicks, you see, will die very fast.

00:34:00.120 --> 00:34:03.320
You have to handle them very, very carefully.

00:34:03.999 --> 00:34:09.400
I am saying this after so many years of not saying this,

00:34:10.999 --> 00:34:13.400
and I am requesting all of you, try to develop.

00:34:13.920 --> 00:34:17.320
Sit before the mirror and try to act like a Mother.

00:34:17.920 --> 00:34:23.920
Let us see, practice it, try to be nice, kindly, gentle, patient.

00:34:24.080 --> 00:34:26.200
If you want to spread Sahaja Yoga in the west,

00:34:26.400 --> 00:34:29.000
we have to do that way. Not in Maharashtra,

00:34:29.200 --> 00:34:32.320
Maharashtra 's mothers are quite strict

00:34:32.480 --> 00:34:36.840
and they are straightforward, and children are used to it.

00:34:36.999 --> 00:34:39.840
You might find that our, you will say that My,

00:34:39.999 --> 00:34:42.999
My Mother was a very strict lady but I think I like her very much

00:34:43.200 --> 00:34:45.999
because she's taught me so many things.

00:34:46.999 --> 00:34:50.120
Other my sisters are expert cooks, we are very good in the life,

00:34:50.320 --> 00:34:53.240
we are doing so well in life, we don't trouble anyone".

00:34:53.480 --> 00:34:55.480
All these things have come from our mother,

00:34:55.999 --> 00:34:57.200
because She was a strict lady

00:34:57.400 --> 00:34:59.840
as she would not tolerate any nonsense.

00:34:59.999 --> 00:35:02.120
She would never tell a lie herself and if you tell her

00:35:02.320 --> 00:35:04.320
"All right, if this gentleman is coming,

00:35:04.480 --> 00:35:07.480
you tell that I am not in the house", "Don't tell me to tell lies.

00:35:07.960 --> 00:35:10.000
I'll tell him that you told me to tell the lies".

00:35:11.280 --> 00:35:13.840
That's how she was

00:35:13.999 --> 00:35:15.999
and that's how she treated us.

00:35:16.160 --> 00:35:18.840
And we lived with that but we didn't mind it

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:21.840
because what she did was for our good.

00:35:21.999 --> 00:35:24.999
We knew that she was doing it for our good.  Not in this country;

00:35:25.200 --> 00:35:27.840
people don't understand this fact.  They have ego.

00:35:27.999 --> 00:35:30.320
They never understand that this is for your good.

00:35:30.480 --> 00:35:32.840
They will always understand this is aggressiveness

00:35:32.999 --> 00:35:35.999
because they themselves are aggressed or they are aggressive.

00:35:36.200 --> 00:35:38.440
If they are aggressed, they are even worse.

00:35:38.960 --> 00:35:42.400
So try to understand what is the situation is in this country.

00:35:42.920 --> 00:35:46.440
I have adjusted Myself; you also should adjust yourself here,

00:35:46.999 --> 00:35:49.999
to the way it is. And that's how I should not hear

00:35:50.160 --> 00:35:52.440
any more any complaints about.

00:35:52.960 --> 00:35:57.960
Now, again the guru tattwa has to go inside, the mother tattwa.

00:36:05.480 --> 00:36:08.440
So next time I will not have any complaints

00:36:08.920 --> 00:36:11.400
but they should all say "Oh, Mother, what a nice man,

00:36:11.960 --> 00:36:15.440
he's so kind, he's so gentle, he's so very sweet".

00:36:16.400 --> 00:36:18.999
It doesn't take at all, anything, to be that.

00:36:19.240 --> 00:36:22.999
Now in this good atmosphere when the nature is so abundant

00:36:23.400 --> 00:36:29.000
and the sun also is hiding its own sharpness,

00:36:29.400 --> 00:36:31.840
where everything is so beautiful,

00:36:31.999 --> 00:36:35.240
we should decide that we will behave in a manner

00:36:35.440 --> 00:36:37.960
that will behoove our Mother.

00:36:38.120 --> 00:36:42.000
and not fight, not quarrel, not say things.

00:36:42.320 --> 00:36:46.999
Like somebody in the train now, supposing going,

00:36:47.200 --> 00:36:49.320
will go and quarrel with the ticket collector?

00:36:49.480 --> 00:36:53.480
"This is my seat, that is mine". A Sahaja Yogi does not do that.

00:36:53.999 --> 00:36:56.200
A Sahaj Yogi, "All right you don't want? All right, I'll sit here.

00:36:56.400 --> 00:36:58.999
All right, whatever is legal I'll do that, whatever is proper I do.

00:36:59.200 --> 00:37:02.480
You want it? All right, doesn't matter. You don't allow? All right".

00:37:02.999 --> 00:37:05.999
Immediately the person melts away.

00:37:06.999 --> 00:37:10.999
But if you, "No, this is my seat.  I've booked it, this, that".

00:37:11.200 --> 00:37:15.320
And then your Mother plays tricks there, on top of that.

00:37:16.999 --> 00:37:20.400
So ultimately you find that the seat was not yours.

00:37:30.080 --> 00:37:33.320
And you, you feel very upset about it,

00:37:33.480 --> 00:37:35.999
"how a Sahaja yogi is insulted"?

00:37:43.999 --> 00:37:46.999
So that is how it is going to work out

00:37:47.320 --> 00:37:50.080
in this beautiful manner

00:37:50.320 --> 00:37:55.320
if we understand the beauty of sweetness

00:37:56.000 --> 00:37:58.840
and beauty of your Mother Earth,

00:37:58.999 --> 00:38:02.920
how She beautifully creates everything.

00:38:03.120 --> 00:38:06.999
And even She is so sweet, I tell you

00:38:07.320 --> 00:38:11.999
that if you are sleeping under a coconut tree, can you imagine now?

00:38:12.280 --> 00:38:16.999
A coconut is so big, if it falls on anybody's head, finished;

00:38:17.160 --> 00:38:19.320
stomach, also, terrible.

00:38:19.480 --> 00:38:23.120
It can break your bone. But it will never fall

00:38:23.360 --> 00:38:27.200
on any human being or any animal. Can you believe it?

00:38:27.999 --> 00:38:30.840
It's a fact. That is the  ritambhara pragya.

00:38:31.000 --> 00:38:33.320
That's the quality of the Mother Earth.

00:38:33.999 --> 00:38:38.999
It never falls on any human being or animal.

00:38:41.999 --> 00:38:43.920
How does She manage that?

00:38:44.080 --> 00:38:47.999
And you have seen how the flowers also form gentle.

00:38:48.480 --> 00:38:50.240
You never see the flowers growing,

00:38:50.440 --> 00:38:53.240
How the Mother does that? Otherwise we'll have problems, you see.

00:38:53.440 --> 00:38:56.480
Suddenly, you see a flower....

00:39:00.999 --> 00:39:06.240
So She, slowly She does it and suddenly you find oh!

00:39:07.999 --> 00:39:10.840
She makes the leaves so beautifully arranged

00:39:10.999 --> 00:39:14.999
that they all get the sun.

00:39:16.400 --> 00:39:17.960
How She manages?

00:39:18.120 --> 00:39:22.840
Then She creates a beautiful shade for you,

00:39:22.999 --> 00:39:26.320
the color scheme, everything so beautiful.

00:39:26.480 --> 00:39:30.440
And then how She nourishes that

00:39:30.960 --> 00:39:32.999
because all the leaves drop down

00:39:33.360 --> 00:39:35.840
and they give nitrogen again to the Mother Earth

00:39:35.999 --> 00:39:38.480
and then She again nourishes them up and they will...

00:39:38.999 --> 00:39:40.280
But the leaves have to fall down

00:39:40.480 --> 00:39:42.999
if the Sun has to come to the Mother Earth.

00:39:44.480 --> 00:39:47.840
It is all Her doing but She does it so beautifully

00:39:47.999 --> 00:39:51.440
that we are not even aware of what She is doing to us.

00:39:53.120 --> 00:39:55.840
We don't know.  If you notice it, the one thing

00:39:55.999 --> 00:39:59.960
about the Mother Earth's beauty that She creates

00:40:00.120 --> 00:40:02.480
and how sweetly She does it,

00:40:02.999 --> 00:40:07.999
you will say that even one billionth of that, if we have,

00:40:08.999 --> 00:40:14.480
