and who holds in Her eighteen hands rosary, axe, mace, arrow,

01:17:15.999 --> 01:17:20.840
thunderbolt, lotus, bow, pitcher, rod,

01:17:20.999 --> 01:17:26.440
shakti, sword, shield, conch, bell, wine-cup,

