So the ladies who have washed My Feet

02:46:07.000 --> 02:46:10.920
and the ones who gave Me saris, please come along.

02:46:18.360 --> 02:46:21.320
Now, you should go and have your lunch I think.

02:46:23.080 --> 02:46:26.480
Noodles, in half an hour you will starve, you see.

02:46:37.920 --> 02:46:40.400
I think I'll give them too. Better.

02:46:49.040 --> 02:46:51.760
SM: I give. You, Esther, got it?
SY: No, Shri Mataji.

02:46:51.960 --> 02:46:54.680
Then you take it.

02:46:55.320 --> 02:46:57.040
Now, take it.

02:46:57.240 --> 02:47:00.440
So if everyone has got it, I am sorry.

02:47:25.160 --> 02:47:27.440
SM: What's that?
SY: Present for You, Mother.

02:47:27.920 --> 02:47:30.040
From you?

02:47:32.840 --> 02:47:37.400
So many hearts. All right, open it.

02:48:09.080 --> 02:48:10.920
So we have eight and this is the ninth.

02:48:11.080 --> 02:48:13.400
We really needed the ninth one.

02:48:23.400 --> 02:48:27.080
Oh, this is the tenth one.

02:48:34.840 --> 02:48:36.840
This is Alsatian, na?

02:48:36.999 --> 02:48:39.160
We will have. And we didn't have this one either.

02:48:39.360 --> 02:48:41.920
SY: Dalmatian, Mother.
SM: What that was?

02:48:42.080 --> 02:48:45.400
Dalmatian? Good. Thank you.

02:48:46.880 --> 02:48:50.280
SY: Now we have ten Mother.
SM: Now, I have ten.

02:48:50.680 --> 02:48:53.320
One more I must get. I'll buy Myself.

02:48:53.640 --> 02:48:57.640
Let My husband buy something for Me.

02:48:57.840 --> 02:49:00.840
These are the bangles for the ladies who are here.

02:49:01.400 --> 02:49:03.840
Very graciously.

02:49:04.400 --> 02:49:06.840
Yogi Mahajan has come all the way from India.

02:49:06.999 --> 02:49:09.880
We have to thank him very much.

02:49:20.040 --> 02:49:23.840
And he has brought these beautiful bangles for the ladies.

02:49:24.000 --> 02:49:27.560
Please, give one each to anyone.

02:49:30.920 --> 02:49:34.480
All right, go ahead for your food. I don't want you to starve.

02:49:34.999 --> 02:49:37.800
What does he want? A doggy?

02:49:38.120 --> 02:49:40.640
Daddy, daddy, Shri Mataji.

02:49:40.840 --> 02:49:42.080
He wants to go to daddy.

02:49:42.280 --> 02:49:45.120
Daddy? Why to daddy?

02:49:48.840 --> 02:49:50.720
You better have some chana.

02:49:51.440 --> 02:49:54.999
All right? Take some chana.

02:49:55.160 --> 02:49:58.240
Daddy doesn't have any chana. Nothing he has.

02:49:58.999 --> 02:50:02.120
You come the other way round.

02:50:02.400 --> 02:50:04.999
Now, take some chana. Come. Little more.

02:50:05.160 --> 02:50:09.320
He can come. Let all the children have the chana.

02:50:09.600 --> 02:50:14.160
All those children who want chana, come here, all right?

02:50:16.999 --> 02:50:21.600
All want chana. That's it.

02:50:27.600 --> 02:50:32.080
That is too small. Which one is there? Come along.

02:50:44.480 --> 02:50:47.280
Here is the chana.

02:50:49.160 --> 02:50:53.920
Child is not well, Rajan. You have to see her. All right?

02:50:56.920 --> 02:50:59.720
SM: Father has come?
SY: Oh, yes, he's come Mother.

02:51:00.040 --> 02:51:03.480
SY: He's feeling well now.
SM: What all the doctors are saying?

02:51:04.920 --> 02:51:06.720
We don't know. Expecting answers.

02:51:06.920 --> 02:51:08.840
Is she all right? I mean, out of danger?

02:51:08.999 --> 02:51:12.640
Yes, she's out of danger now. Just she'll maybe go home today.

02:51:12.840 --> 02:51:13.840
Oh that's good.

02:51:13.999 --> 02:51:15.560
Just, just five minutes ago,

02:51:15.760 --> 02:51:17.840
someone has phoned from the hospital Shri Mataji,

02:51:17.999 --> 02:51:20.720
that they can be fetched in a car from there.

02:51:20.920 --> 02:51:24.480
She can be fetched. That's good. That's like a Sahaja Yogini.

02:51:24.960 --> 02:51:27.999
All right, but now I would suggest that when she goes back

02:51:28.160 --> 02:51:31.360
let her stay here for a while and then go all the ladies,

02:51:31.600 --> 02:51:32.999
let them go by train.

02:51:33.200 --> 02:51:36.240
And [if it's somebody's] little van is too small.

02:51:36.480 --> 02:51:38.720
And next time it should be a law,

02:51:38.920 --> 02:51:42.720
anybody carrying a child in the lap is not allowed to come.

02:51:42.920 --> 02:51:45.120
All right? That is the status to be able to walk around

02:51:45.320 --> 02:51:46.760
and not in such a way.

02:51:46.960 --> 02:51:48.760
One should not do this way.

02:51:48.960 --> 02:51:51.680
And pregnant women are not allowed at all to come.

02:51:52.160 --> 02:51:55.800
You know that. That's not to be agreed to

02:51:55.999 --> 02:51:57.560
at any cost, whatever it is, you see.

02:51:57.760 --> 02:52:00.280
It's very dangerous, it worries Me.

02:52:00.680 --> 02:52:02.960
Thank God she is all right because of Sahaja Yoga.

02:52:03.120 --> 02:52:05.320
She's perfectly all right and she comes back home.

02:52:05.600 --> 02:52:08.680
So that's a good thing. Come.

02:52:11.080 --> 02:52:14.400
But next time make it a point, please make it a point.

02:52:18.880 --> 02:52:22.640
Only flowers.

02:52:27.720 --> 02:52:30.280
SM: Have I given you already.
SY: Yes.

02:52:30.600 --> 02:52:36.080
So, try to understand that, you see, the pregnancy,

02:52:36.400 --> 02:52:38.720
you have to be very careful.

02:52:38.920 --> 02:52:43.160
If you have your own car, all right, if you can have [unclear]

02:52:44.080 --> 02:52:46.999
if you can travel with someone else, it's all right.

02:52:48.160 --> 02:52:49.880
That too in early pregnancy

02:52:50.040 --> 02:52:52.400
not in the very advanced pregnancy.

02:52:52.680 --> 02:52:56.920
Because you have come here to help Me in a way,

02:52:57.999 --> 02:53:00.160
and also to get help from Me.

02:53:00.360 --> 02:53:04.320
But if you come during pregnancy at a very advanced stage

02:53:04.600 --> 02:53:07.600
it can create a problem, you see.

02:53:08.040 --> 02:53:12.360
So be careful not to do such a thing anymore.

02:53:12.720 --> 02:53:15.960
And if there are ladies travelling,

02:53:16.160 --> 02:53:18.960
it's better they travel by train with small children,

02:53:19.120 --> 02:53:22.320
but never a child who is not yet walking.

02:53:23.200 --> 02:53:27.160
If the child is not walking the ladies must stay at home.

02:53:28.680 --> 02:53:32.320
Please remember that, it's a law, that we do not allow

02:53:32.560 --> 02:53:34.999
anybody to come to India with the children.

02:53:35.160 --> 02:53:38.560
Now, if you have got children, and you want to come to India,

02:53:38.760 --> 02:53:40.800
then do only one small thing.

02:53:40.999 --> 02:53:44.880
You notify that you want, "we have got children" and

02:53:45.320 --> 02:53:49.400
we could find out some crèche in Switzerland,

02:53:49.840 --> 02:53:54.240
in Rome, in England, anywhere,

02:53:54.760 --> 02:53:59.000
for these children to be left there. And you can come free,

02:53:59.600 --> 02:54:01.960
freely there. That is important.

02:54:02.160 --> 02:54:05.960
But if the child is very small, I would say, don't come.

02:54:06.440 --> 02:54:09.400
But even children are not to be brought to India.

02:54:09.880 --> 02:54:13.280
So all the children can be kept there. It is during holiday time,

02:54:13.600 --> 02:54:15.440
we are having this time the program.

02:54:15.760 --> 02:54:18.760
So please do not bring children to India.

02:54:19.080 --> 02:54:22.999
Try to keep the children. They can be kept somewhere, not difficult.

02:54:24.240 --> 02:54:27.960
We can form some crèche in the ashrams and we can manage that.

02:54:30.080 --> 02:54:32.200
All right. So now and have your food.

02:54:32.440 --> 02:54:34.240
Somebody must go and keep the door open.

02:54:34.440 --> 02:54:36.240
Please put your hand in the door.

02:54:36.440 --> 02:54:40.200
Shri Mataji, this is the last Puja, for the whole tour of Europe.

02:54:40.480 --> 02:54:43.640
From all the Sahaja Yogis we want to thank you for the tremendous,

02:54:43.800 --> 02:54:48.360
beautifully, enjoible tour that you gave us all. Jai Shri Mataji.
